BuildRequires:    R-devel
Requires:         R-core
BuildArch:        noarch

%description
Implements an algorithm for efficient and exact calculation of
hypergeometric and binomial probabilities using Chebyshev polynomials,
while other algorithm use an approximation when N is large. A useful
applications is also considered in this package for the construction of
attribute sampling plans which is an important field of statistical
quality control. The quantile, and the confidence limit for the attribute
sampling plan are also implemented in this package. The hypergeometric
distribution can be represented in terms of Chebyshev polynomials. This
representation is particularly useful in the calculation of exact values
of hypergeometric variables.

